actions.message: It’s a lovely night, isn’t it my friend? The moon has risen.
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message:
The hot breath of the hounds, it chases you. No matter where, no matter when.
Does it make you fearful? Does it make you scared? It will never end. I know it doesn’t.
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message: This mistake of mine, this mistake of ours. The midnight flowers grow on fields of bone, watered by our sins.
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message: Do you like the song? I made it for them. And the poem, well, that’s for you. I’m not very good at playing the piano, though.
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message: Why the poem? Because we will never be allowed to forget. We must well make paint from the pigment. No use in dwelling it what could be. But it can still be beautiful, no?
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message: Why that look? Ah, I see. You’ve forgotten, haven’t you? Forgotten me….No matter. Though, I can’t agree with...that taste in fashion. Haha.
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message: No matter. I hope you wont forget to read the logs, or the terms of contract. That would be troublesome, wouldn’t it?

actions.message: Ah, I miss you already. But....
